description: This is a 100% **FREE** NFT that will be given away to the first 50 people who follow me on Showtime. The 50 blocks represent the individual people who will eventually own this piece and the new colorful art we will all be bringing into each other’s lives by simply connecting through Showtime. Feel free to swap or burn. Enjoy!  Created by @JimmyTheGhost.
